content: Discussed enterprise requirements and pricing structure. Sarah is interested in the premium package.
Sent proposal document and implementation timeline. Waiting for feedback from their technical team.
Initial discovery meeting completed. Identified key pain points in their current system.
David mentioned they're evaluating 3 different CRM solutions. Need to emphasize our unique value proposition.
Follow-up call to address security concerns. Provided additional documentation on data encryption.
Project completed successfully. Lisa was very happy with the final deliverables.
